Package: replicateEverything
Title: Replicate Empirical Research Papers
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Macartan", "Humphreys", email = "macartan.humphreys@wzb.eu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Vermon", "Washington", email = "vermon.washington@wzb.eu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
)
Description: Tools for discovering and running computational replications of empirical research papers. 
    The package connects to a replication registry, retrieves replication materials 
    (data, code, and metadata), and reproduces figures and tables from published studies.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports: 
    jsonlite,
    yaml,
    utils
